title: Roy Haynes April 1996
description: Leigh talks to Roy during a gig at the Artists Quarter in St. Paul MN about subjects including a reissue of his early quartet record Out of The Afternoon with Rahsaan Roland Kirk and a tune he did that Billie Holliday recored.  They also talk about Boston band leader Sabby Lewis and Roy's interest in Sugar Ray Leonard and professional boxing.
